{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.1","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:1","prev_osis_id":"Deut.012.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.013.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Punition de l\u2019idol\u00e2trie au milieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-5: cf. (Mt 24:24. 2 Th 2:9-12.) (J\u00e9 23:9, etc. 2 Pi 2:1-3.) (1 Jn 4:1-6. Ga 1:8.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.13.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>S\u2019il s\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8ve au milieu de toi un proph\u00e8te ou un songeur qui t\u2019annonce un signe ou un prodige,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.2","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:2","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.12.32","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 12:32","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.12.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.2","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:2","prev_osis_id":"Deut.013.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.013.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.13.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>et qu\u2019il y ait accomplissement du signe ou du prodige dont il t\u2019a parl\u00e9 en disant: Allons apr\u00e8s d\u2019autres dieux, des dieux que tu ne connais point, et servons-les!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.3","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:3","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.1","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:1","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.3","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:3","prev_osis_id":"Deut.013.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.013.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.13.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>tu n\u2019\u00e9couteras pas les paroles de ce proph\u00e8te ou de ce songeur, car c\u2019est l\u2019\u00c9ternel, votre Dieu, qui vous met \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9preuve pour savoir si vous aimez l\u2019\u00c9ternel, votre Dieu, de tout votre c\u0153ur et de toute votre \u00e2me.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.2","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:2","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.4","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:4","prev_osis_id":"Deut.013.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.013.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.13.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Vous irez apr\u00e8s l\u2019\u00c9ternel, votre Dieu, et vous le craindrez; vous observerez ses commandements, vous ob\u00e9irez \u00e0 sa voix, vous le servirez, et vous vous attacherez \u00e0 lui.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.5","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:5","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.3","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:3","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.5","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:5","prev_osis_id":"Deut.013.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.013.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.13.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Ce proph\u00e8te ou ce songeur sera puni de mort, car il a parl\u00e9 de r\u00e9volte contre l\u2019\u00c9ternel, votre Dieu, qui vous a fait sortir du pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte et vous a d\u00e9livr\u00e9s de la maison de servitude, et il a voulu te d\u00e9tourner de la voie dans laquelle l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, t\u2019a ordonn\u00e9 de marcher. Tu \u00f4teras ainsi le mal du milieu de toi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.6","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:6","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.4","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:4","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.6","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:6","prev_osis_id":"Deut.013.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.013.007,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 6-11: cf. De 17:2-7. Mt 10:34-37.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.13.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Si ton fr\u00e8re, fils de ta m\u00e8re, ou ton fils, ou ta fille, ou la femme qui repose sur ton sein, ou ton ami que tu aimes comme toi-m\u00eame, t\u2019incite secr\u00e8tement en disant: Allons, et servons d\u2019autres dieux! Des dieux que ni toi ni tes p\u00e8res n\u2019avez connus,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.5","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:5","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.7","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:7","prev_osis_id":"Deut.013.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.013.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.13.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>d\u2019entre les dieux des peuples qui vous entourent, pr\u00e8s de toi ou loin de toi, d\u2019une extr\u00e9mit\u00e9 de la terre \u00e0 l\u2019autre,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.8","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:8","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.6","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:6","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.8","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:8","prev_osis_id":"Deut.013.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.013.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.13.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>tu n\u2019y consentiras pas, et tu ne l\u2019\u00e9couteras pas; tu ne jetteras pas sur lui un regard de piti\u00e9, tu ne l\u2019\u00e9pargneras pas, et tu ne le couvriras pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.9","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:9","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.7","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:7","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.9","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:9","prev_osis_id":"Deut.013.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.013.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.13.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Mais tu le feras mourir; ta main se l\u00e8vera la premi\u00e8re sur lui pour le mettre \u00e0 mort, et la main de tout le peuple ensuite;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.10","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:10","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.8","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:8","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.10","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:10","prev_osis_id":"Deut.013.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.013.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.13.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>tu le lapideras, et il mourra, parce qu\u2019il a cherch\u00e9 \u00e0 te d\u00e9tourner de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, qui t\u2019a fait sortir du pays d\u2019\u00c9gypte, de la maison de servitude.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.11","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:11","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.9","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:9","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.11","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:11","prev_osis_id":"Deut.013.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.013.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.13.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Il en sera ainsi, afin que tout Isra\u00ebl entende et craigne, et que l\u2019on ne commette plus un acte aussi criminel au milieu de toi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.12","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:12","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.10","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:10","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.12","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:12","prev_osis_id":"Deut.013.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.013.013,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 12-18: cf. (Jos 22:11-20. Jg 20.) Jos 6:17-26.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.13.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Si tu entends dire au sujet de l\u2019une des villes que t\u2019a donn\u00e9es pour demeure l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.11","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:11","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.13","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:13","prev_osis_id":"Deut.013.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.013.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.13.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Des gens pervers sont sortis du milieu de toi, et ont s\u00e9duit les habitants de leur ville en disant: Allons, et servons d\u2019autres dieux! Des dieux que tu ne connais point<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.14","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:14","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.12","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:12","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.14","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:14","prev_osis_id":"Deut.013.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.013.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.13.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>tu feras des recherches, tu examineras, tu interrogeras avec soin. La chose est-elle vraie, le fait est-il \u00e9tabli, cette abomination a-t-elle \u00e9t\u00e9 commise au milieu de toi,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.15","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:15","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.15","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:15","prev_osis_id":"Deut.013.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.013.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.13.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>alors tu frapperas du tranchant de l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e les habitants de cette ville, tu la d\u00e9voueras par interdit avec tout ce qui s\u2019y trouvera, et tu en passeras le b\u00e9tail au fil de l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.16","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:16","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.14","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:14","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.16","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:16","prev_osis_id":"Deut.013.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.013.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.13.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Tu amasseras tout le butin au milieu de la place, et tu br\u00fbleras enti\u00e8rement au feu la ville avec tout son butin, devant l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu: elle sera pour toujours un monceau de ruines, elle ne sera jamais reb\u00e2tie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.17","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:17","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.15","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:15","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.17","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:17","prev_osis_id":"Deut.013.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.013.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.13.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Rien de ce qui sera d\u00e9vou\u00e9 par interdit ne s\u2019attachera \u00e0 ta main, afin que l\u2019\u00c9ternel revienne de l\u2019ardeur de sa col\u00e8re, qu\u2019il te fasse mis\u00e9ricorde et gr\u00e2ce, et qu\u2019il te multiplie, comme il l\u2019a jur\u00e9 \u00e0 tes p\u00e8res,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.18","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:18","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.16","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:16","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.18","label":"","reference":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:18","prev_osis_id":"Deut.013.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Deut.014.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Deut.13.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>si tu ob\u00e9is \u00e0 la voix de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, en observant tous ses commandements que je te prescris aujourd\u2019hui, et en faisant ce qui est droit aux yeux de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Deut.13","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.14.1","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 14:1","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.14.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Deut.13.17","name":"Deut\u00e9ronome 13:17","id":"fra-LSG:Deut.13.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fb1eee084.54819389');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb1eee084.54819389\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fb1eee084.54819389","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fb1eee084.54819389'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fb1eee084.54819389\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}